title: r/Prorevenge He Took My Trees, So I Took ALL His Money... It's TREE LAW!
description:
r/Prorevenge I think it's been a while since we've had a tree law video. Are you ready for the sweet, delicious justice of tree law? If you've never seen a tree law video before, then prepare yourself, because it turns out that trees are expensive... VERY expensive. Cutting down your neighbor's trees could mean that you owe literally millions of dollars. This douchebag neighbor who threatens to kill OP's dog makes the worst mistake of his life when he cuts down trees on OP's property! If you like this podcast and you want to see more, follow my podcast for more daily Reddit content!
